    "GlmMoeDsaForCausalLM": {
      "_source": "https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/zh-cn/latest/tutorials/models/GLM5.2.html (A2 4P4D) + GLM5.html",
      "_fix": "2026-06-13 对齐官方 GLM5 PD：max_model_len 拆角色级(P=131072/D=200000)；P 关 prefix/compilation 加 enforce_eager；D 关 prefix/chunked 补 capture_sizes；补 tool/reasoning parser；additional_config 补 recompute/enable_dsa_cp。compilation_config=null 表示该角色应删除 base 注入的图捕获。2026-06-16 fresh 核对当前线上官方 P 命令已无 layer_sharding，故移除（仅 GLM5 P；V3.2 不受影响）。2026-06-25 严格对齐官方 GLM5.2 A2 4P4D：connector 换 MooncakeConnector(kv_p2p)+connector_module_path；两端 additional_config 补 enable_sparse_c8=false；common 补 async_scheduling；decode 改 164/48、删 cudagraph_capture_sizes；两端 env 删 VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2；common_env 补 HCCL_OP_EXPANSION_MODE=AIV/VLLM_VERSION=0.21.0/ASCEND_TRANSPORT_PRINT=1、删 VLLM_MOONCAKE_ABORT_REQUEST_TIMEOUT；P.env 补 HCCL_BUFFSIZE=256/VLLM_NIXL_ABORT_REQUEST_TIMEOUT=300000，D.env 补 HCCL_BUFFSIZE=500。engine_id/kv_port 偏移/block_size/rpc-port/--host 维持现状(与官方功能等价)。2026-06-25 strip_env(A2)：剔除官方不设的 6 个多余 env(VLLM_USE_V1/VLLM_LLMDD_RPC_PORT/VLLM_MOONCAKE_BOOTSTRAP_PORT/ASCEND_CONNECT_TIMEOUT/ASCEND_TRANSFER_TIMEOUT/ASCEND_A3_ENABLE)，P 另剔 TASK_QUEUE_ENABLE(官方 P 不设/D 保留)，VLLM_MOONCAKE_BOOTSTRAP_PORT 连 fork 内联一并省去。",
      "connector": "MooncakeConnector",
      "connector_module_path": "vllm_ascend.distributed.kv_transfer.kv_p2p.mooncake_connector",
      "kv_port": { "P": "30000", "D": "30100" },
      "default_platform": "a2",
      "extra_config": { "use_ascend_direct": true },
      "common_env": {
        "ASCEND_AGGREGATE_ENABLE": "1",
        "ACL_OP_INIT_MODE": "1",
